			content of scholarly journals, is a public good. Public goods are free to
			consume, and therefore, access to scholarly journals should be free as
			well.
		</p>

		<p style="text-align:justify" class="margin-p">
			Aaron’s Kit captures the vision of Aaron Swartz. Our project is your
			project and by joining forces, we can continue Aaron’s legacy — to
			transform the antiquated system of academic publishing into an Open Access
